Defendant Naeem Robert Bradley in court with Attorney Danielle L. Shelton.  Defendant Naeem Robert Bradley in custody.  Maureen Ami Atwell appeared for the State of Wisconsin.  

Statements made by the parties as to the sentencing.  The Court had a side bar conversation with counsels.

Court ordered Defendant held in the Milwaukee County Jail until turned over to Justice Point.   The Court CONVERTED the $500 cash bail to a $500 PR bond with TURNOVER to Justice Point Pretrial Services for supervision. Standard rules of Justice Point to apply along with the following rules:

*JusticePoint Supervision once a week;
*Alcohol and Drug Free;
*Work Search Every Day - 5 employers and bring proof to the Court at next court date;
*Cannot leave the State of Wisconsin;
*No Potowami or any other gambling facility;

The matter is adjourned for a review hearing on September 3, 2015 at 8:30am in Br. 30, Judge Conen's court.  Deputy Court Clerk tg
